== Overview message receive ==

com.googlecode.asmack.chat.StanzaReceiver
registered via AndroidManifest.xml

StanzaReceiver <- Database.getDatabase
StanzaReceiver.onReceive
- filters the input (only <message>, ...)
- creates ContentValues
- stores the ContentValues into the database

== Overview jabber chat start ==

com.googlecode.asmack.chat.Chat
registered via AndroidManifest.xml

Uses AutoscrollListView with HistoryCursorAdapter to show the chat history.

== General ==

Please respect the goal of keeping this app simple but functional.
